snippet.title: DOGS, super FUNNY, you will LAUGH! - Funny DOG VIDEOS compilation
snippet.description:
Funny dogs and puppies never fail to make us laugh and happy! They are the best! This funny dog compilation is a super hard TRY NOT TO LAUGH challenge! Just look how all these dogs and puppies behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
